nodes.bodyText: if this if (uri) comes first then no need another if, if (!uri)  can be removed
Semantically it would make more sense to pass the subroutine list before the mode because the mode in most cases will be the same.
I see you miss a test for it. Not a big deal though, but we miss coverage here.
